PRIVACY POLICY FOR NEYO  ON QUEST 2, QUEST PRO, AND QUEST 3
Neyo is an application developed by VisioPlan Solutions GmbH for the Meta Quest platform. We prioritize your privacy and are committed to complying with all applicable privacy regulations, including the European Union's General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). The application is designed as an online, solo experience, which require internet connection. The Neyo application does not collect any personal information, data, or statistics.

COMMITMENT TO CONFIDENTIALITY
VisioPlan Solutions GmbH is committed to safeguarding your privacy while you use Neyo on the Meta Quest platform. Below are the key points of our privacy policy:

Confidential Information
"Confidential Information" refers to any data or information exchanged between VisioPlan Solutions GmbH and the user in any form (though in the context of this application, no such exchange takes place). We guarantee that no personal data will be collected by Neyo.

Ownership and Use of Data
Any information related to your use of the application will remain entirely private. We do not transmit, sell, or monetize any data. No third-party providers will have access to any information.

Duration of the Agreement
This privacy agreement is effective from the moment you download and install Ghost Hunter. The terms of this agreement will remain in effect for as long as you use the game, and since no data is collected, your privacy is always maintained.

Governing Law and Jurisdiction
This privacy policy is governed by the laws applicable in your country of residence, and any disputes related to this policy will be handled under the relevant legal jurisdictions.

USER RIGHTS & DATA PROTECTION
As Neyo does not collect, store, or process any personal data, you maintain full control over your information. There are no user rights to exercise in relation to personal data, as we do not request or handle any such information.

DATA TRANSMISSION
There is no transmission of personal data when using Neyo. The application requires an internet connection to receive the content displayed in the Neyo application. No personal or game-related information is ever transmitted to us or any third party.

HOW WE PROTECT YOUR PRIVACY
VisioPlan Solutions GmbH is dedicated to ensuring that your privacy is respected throughout your experience with Neyo. Specifically, we guarantee that:

No data, including personal or statistical information, is collected.
No personal information is shared or communicated with any third parties.
